{"tid":474470,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡雲尼：12碼以後畀尼馬射","createTime":"2017-11-20T07:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T14:47:16.000Z","uid":10016,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cc238c5e818d3bae87469c413420ecf018b91683","tid":474470,"uid":10016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"尼馬和卡雲尼曾經爭射12碼，不過卡雲尼現在態度軟化，決定以後將巴黎聖日耳門的12碼讓給尼馬操刀。<br />\n<br />\n季初比賽PSG以2：0擊敗里昂，那場比賽的話題卻是尼馬與卡雲尼爭射12碼。<br />\n那次爭射是卡雲尼搶贏，不過他卻射失了。<br />\n<br />\n現在12碼風波已經平息，因為卡雲尼決定將12碼讓給尼馬操刀。當被問及下次12碼讓誰人射時，卡雲尼說：「尼馬。」<br />\n泰亞高施華說：「我們全隊決定了，以後的12碼全部讓給尼馬射吧。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=K0mr2195hrbrTEs%2BuxJlBgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=332b9e20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"0c9a891f3cf20ba100e675fcd2b9ccce3a610df6","tid":474470,"uid":107472,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"b2d0978bed55846c2b46df3c8e432f9a6cd98d94","tid":474470,"uid":153600,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"尼馬真係以為自己係大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果伊巴仲係度佢仲邊敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7e1d93149dcad1a7cdef7dce88f2ae1f9b637c","tid":474470,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"槍口對外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9659d4ede989c5febafda537894a0f022fba79bd","tid":474470,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尼馬真係以為自己係大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果伊巴仲係度佢仲邊敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係度又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地班主 2億買返來 